title: Contributing
content:
To contribute to this wonderful site, go to [our GitHub](https://github.com/PgBiel/saltbotpages) and slap that [`New Pull Request` button](https://github.com/PgBiel/saltbotpages/compare), and send us a yummy munchy pull request with whatever you want updated *(just make sure it's not announcements.json)*!  
**Keep in mind that:**  
 - [`messages.json`](https://pgbiel.github.io/saltbotpages/info/messages.json) are where the messages are located  
 - You should test your code before making a pull request
